575
00:32:02,519 --> 00:32:03,839
That's right. How nice is that?

576
00:32:04,200 --> 00:32:05,200
Let's drink.

577
00:32:05,319 --> 00:32:06,319
Everyone is holding a glass.

578
00:32:11,799 --> 00:32:14,640
It's rare that my parents don't argue when they are together.

579
00:32:14,640 --> 00:32:15,680
Thank you.

580
00:32:17,160 --> 00:32:18,359
Have you ever done a puzzle?

581
00:32:19,039 --> 00:32:20,079
No.

582
00:32:20,440 --> 00:32:21,799
Then you must have seen someone playing it.

583
00:32:22,640 --> 00:32:23,720
Of course.

584
00:32:24,640 --> 00:32:26,640
