589
00:32:33,559 --> 00:32:36,279
Actually, it's not that this piece of the puzzle is great.

590
00:32:36,559 --> 00:32:39,119
It's just a coincidence that it fits.

591
00:32:40,960 --> 00:32:42,400
You haven't changed since school.

592
00:32:42,680 --> 00:32:44,519
You are brainy and full of ideas.

593
00:32:47,599 --> 00:32:50,279
Do you think there's any chance of them getting back together?

594
00:32:51,480 --> 00:32:52,880
I didn't think it was possible.

595
00:32:53,119 --> 00:32:55,160
But since my mom is here today,

596
00:32:56,000 --> 00:32:57,240
