597
00:32:57,680 --> 00:32:58,960
My mom is so proud.

598
00:32:59,960 --> 00:33:01,319
It doesn't matter how arrogant one is.

599
00:33:01,559 --> 00:33:02,759
They are willing to give in...

600
00:33:02,759 --> 00:33:04,240
for their children.

601
00:33:05,880 --> 00:33:07,200
Look at Mr. Wu today.

602
00:33:07,480 --> 00:33:09,279
He prepared all of your mom's favorite dishes.

603
00:33:09,279 --> 00:33:10,359
He even bought flowers.

604
00:33:10,599 --> 00:33:11,599
You noticed that.

605
00:33:12,079 --> 00:33:13,519
I thought I was the main character.

606
00:33:13,519 --> 00:33:15,440
- But I was just a third wheel. - Who isn't?

607
00:33:17,640 --> 00:33:19,319
But today was just the beginning.

608
00:33:19,480 --> 00:33:20,640
For them,

609
00:33:21,200 --> 00:33:22,640
