610
00:33:23,440 --> 00:33:24,480
I hope so.

611
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:26,480
That's enough.

612
00:33:26,799 --> 00:33:28,319
- Go back to them. - Okay.

613
00:33:28,440 --> 00:33:29,599
I've got to go. Bye.

614
00:33:48,400 --> 00:33:50,000
I'll do it, Dad.

615
00:33:50,160 --> 00:33:51,200
It's okay.

616
00:33:51,720 --> 00:33:52,759
Go and check on your mom.

617
00:33:52,880 --> 00:33:53,880
She's not feeling well.

618
00:34:01,240 --> 00:34:03,079
Mom, are you all right?

619
00:34:04,279 --> 00:34:05,279
It's okay.

620
00:34:07,559 --> 00:34:10,079
I didn't drink that much.

621
00:34:10,079 --> 00:34:11,920
Why am I so dizzy?

622
00:34:13,769 --> 00:34:14,920
I'm such a party pooper.

623
00:34:15,400 --> 00:34:17,119
It's fine. There's no one else.

624
00:34:17,840 --> 00:34:19,480
Did Lan Qi leave?

625
00:34:19,719 --> 00:34:20,719
He did.

626
00:34:21,000 --> 00:34:22,119
Shi Yi.

627
00:34:22,360 --> 00:34:26,159
I told you that he's a good man.

628
00:34:26,159 --> 00:34:28,960
