629
00:34:30,769 --> 00:34:33,289
Mom, why don't you stay here tonight?

630
00:34:33,289 --> 00:34:34,679
Let my dad take good care of you.

631
00:34:35,159 --> 00:34:36,360
No.

632
00:34:37,039 --> 00:34:38,079
I have to go.

633
00:34:38,679 --> 00:34:39,679
Help me up.

634
00:34:40,039 --> 00:34:41,519
