636
00:34:43,880 --> 00:34:45,360
Your dad's pillow stinks!

637
00:34:45,360 --> 00:34:47,599
I don't know when the last time he washed it.

638
00:34:48,199 --> 00:34:49,329
Let's go.

639
00:34:49,329 --> 00:34:50,400
Be careful.

640
00:34:54,039 --> 00:34:55,079
Easy.

641
00:34:55,360 --> 00:34:56,920
- Turn to the side. - Turn to the side.

642
00:34:59,360 --> 00:35:00,440
Turn.

643
00:35:00,440 --> 00:35:01,880
- Go around. - Turn.

644
00:35:02,679 --> 00:35:03,769
My goodness.

645
00:35:04,440 --> 00:35:05,519
My goodness.

646
00:35:06,719 --> 00:35:07,809
His feet.

647
00:35:08,329 --> 00:35:10,480
Don't you know your limit?

648
00:35:10,809 --> 00:35:11,840
You're so drunk.

649
00:35:14,559 --> 00:35:15,599
I'm exhausted.

650
00:35:15,880 --> 00:35:16,880
Monkey.

651
00:35:19,239 --> 00:35:20,289
Boss.

652
00:35:20,559 --> 00:35:22,119
Didn't he say he wanted to go to Shenzhen?

653
00:35:22,719 --> 00:35:23,809
