708
00:39:14,679 --> 00:39:15,840
I didn't mean anything by it.

709
00:39:16,400 --> 00:39:17,769
Don't tell Shi Yi.

710
00:39:18,809 --> 00:39:20,329
Let's respect his decision.

711
00:39:21,079 --> 00:39:22,239
Or else,

712
00:39:22,769 --> 00:39:24,289
