713
00:39:29,679 --> 00:39:31,679
I just want one less person to misunderstand him.

714
00:39:34,880 --> 00:39:36,000
He's pretty manly.

715
00:39:36,769 --> 00:39:37,960
Okay.

716
00:39:38,719 --> 00:39:39,769
I got it.

717
00:40:07,719 --> 00:40:08,880
